6:
Sound the alarms, blow the bugles,
we have an emergency!
20: There's a head, Alk! There's a HEEEAD!
26: What? S-stop it! You're scaring me!
31:
It's a monster! A magical head
monster!
35:
It's lurking in the Kaleidoscope, but I
have NEVER, EVER seen anything like
it before!
39:
Doesn't that just mean a shift
brought it here from another world?
What's got you so freaked out?
43:
It's that I don't get what world
could've created such a
monstrosity. Like, it's obvious it's
from some advanced civilization
'cause it looks super high-tech and
kinda... valuable?
45:
But jeepers, this thing is basically
the reigning overlord of uncanny
valley...
53:
So the head is made out of gold.
And when unsuspecting
adventurers wander up to it... its
eyes light up.
55:
And EVERYONE that it defeats in
battle is goldenized.
63:
But here's the clincher! The head
ABSORBS the glistening body of its
enemies and then visibly GROWS.
68:
What a terrifying beast. One can
only guess at its true purpose.
72:
Okay, but if it's really that strong,
why hasn't the Guild sent in troops
of master adventurers?
79:
So we're actually worried that
broadcasting the existence of this
insanely freaky monster could
cause widespread panic.
83:
But you guys have already seen
some pretty weird stuff, right? So
you guys should be able to keep it
together, RIGHT?!
87:
What do you two think? Are we
doing this?
92:
We may be walking into the jaws of
death, but I should be ashamed to
turn tail and run.
98: I want to see the disembodied head.
105:
That's the spirit! I knew you guys
wouldn't let me down!
107:
Now, I'll take care of the paperwork,
so it's straight off to the
Kaleidoscope with you.
111:
Oh right. So apparently, the monster
calls itself C. F. Kiseki. The C. F.
stands for "crowdfunding."
114:
It's apparently some new way to
make money? I don't know, but the
person who first found the head
said it's popular where they're from.
119:
I guess that sort of explains why it
turns people into gold...
122:
Yeah. And one more thing.
Apparently, the head talks. In, like,
this super energetic girl's voice.
